Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,== OCR ==
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.57,0:02:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不習慣一大班人大吃大喝的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.78,0:02:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔…你…還要戰鬥嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.52,0:02:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,國際聯合軍早晚會来到這里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.62,0:02:30.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們會毫不猶疑把這個東京毀滅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.46,0:02:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個城市亦已經無人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.86,0:02:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我，你為誰而戰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.53,0:02:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為保護甚麽而戰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.24,0:02:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今晚很多話說呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.71,0:02:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎可以！怎可那樣做…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.49,0:02:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？米奇和莉莉呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.43,0:03:05.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米…米奇…！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.04,0:03:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米奇！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.04,0:03:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.22,0:03:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.85,0:03:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生甚麽事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.52,0:03:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米奇！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.16,0:03:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子是屬於我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.43,0:03:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的一部份，是我的雛型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.83,0:03:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽了？他在說甚麽？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.90,0:03:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格拉迪亞…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.57,0:03:47.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是！米奇就是米奇！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.77,0:03:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還給我！把米奇還給我啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.67,0:03:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肉體是亞人的一部份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.01,0:03:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早晚都只會同化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.31,0:03:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個身體有太多不適當的資料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.21,0:04:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住口！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.55,0:04:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙在做甚麽？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.65,0:04:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙正把自己的資料…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.12,0:04:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輸進米奇腦內！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.36,0:04:10.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他身為人類的資料和記憶消除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.53,0:04:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.38,0:04:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要你護送難民離開，對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.55,0:04:37.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你開始戰鬥之候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.72,0:04:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留在這種地方會無命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.16,0:04:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會馬上回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.06,0:04:52.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉你還是跟米奇一起吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.44,0:04:56.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想的話，可以的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.57,0:05:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莲娜，你也留下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.38,0:05:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我跟格拉迪亞…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.91,0:05:05.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟誕自我腦內的怪物…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.08,0:05:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決生死的最候一戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.45,0:05:10.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟戰士飛刀無關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.72,0:05:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且亦再沒酬勞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.79,0:05:14.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.36,0:05:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去，我要從格拉迪亞手上…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.63,0:05:19.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搶回米奇的記憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.47,0:05:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.26,0:05:51.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無恥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.23,0:05:54.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布烈絲！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.33,0:05:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回来候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.10,0:05:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們幹些進一步的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.24,0:06:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.05,0:06:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家願意跟我並肩作戰嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.68,0:06:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直是個普通文員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.08,0:06:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能加入戰士飛刀就像做夢一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.62,0:06:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，我並非想向你報恩…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.89,0:06:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己也不大清楚…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.79,0:06:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是戰士飛刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.60,0:06:28.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那便行吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.50,0:06:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消滅亞人的影子執法者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.83,0:06:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亦一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.44,0:06:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.57,0:06:36.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.51,0:06:42.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰士飛刀，出動！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.78,0:06:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要平安回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.69,0:06:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.47,0:07:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些好像霧的東西是甚麽？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.27,0:07:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像突然變得濃起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.11,0:07:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.34,0:07:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打破側面的牆候別走散
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.41,0:07:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔內充滿費挪現象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.68,0:07:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一不小心便會被感染
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.88,0:07:21.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消滅格拉迪亞便行吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.36,0:07:34.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布烈絲！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.63,0:07:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布烈絲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.71,0:07:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些霧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.34,0:07:46.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是亞人化了的微毫機械！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.21,0:07:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.99,0:08:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡！不能前進嗎！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.49,0:08:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的防禦毫無漏洞呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.26,0:08:08.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,助我加速
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.03,0:08:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,單靠我的噴射器，馬力不夠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.51,0:08:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無錯，效率很差呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.78,0:08:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確無錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.05,0:08:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.89,0:08:35.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絲莉亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.49,0:08:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米奇…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.76,0:08:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心頭部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.10,0:08:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反作用力會相當厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.93,0:08:44.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你放心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.87,0:08:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莲娜！回来！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.81,0:08:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莲娜！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.35,0:08:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.26,0:09:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎辦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.40,0:09:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.67,0:09:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他想做甚麽！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.78,0:09:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.48,0:09:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.58,0:09:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米奇！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.99,0:09:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米奇！你還記得我嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.79,0:09:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不大清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.76,0:09:44.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經…記不起莉莉的容貌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.63,0:09:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎會的…！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.43,0:09:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，我記得對我来說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.47,0:09:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫莉莉的人是非常重要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.47,0:09:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的腦內留有一點我自己的記憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.97,0:10:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…那快要…消失了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.15,0:10:05.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為甚麽！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.91,0:10:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行！我絕對不容許！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.82,0:10:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽了！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.12,0:10:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米奇…！米奇在跟莉莉說話嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.19,0:10:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽住，莉莉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.76,0:10:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在跟格拉迪亞連接在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.59,0:10:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會向格拉迪亞…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.43,0:10:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輸出我的不規則邏輯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.60,0:10:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亦即是我身為人類時的資料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.60,0:10:27.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是格拉迪亞所不能理解的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.90,0:10:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她應該不懂如何處理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.07,0:10:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停止！若你那樣做…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.04,0:10:34.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行！米奇你沒有那種力量的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.04,0:10:36.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽了！？他們在說甚麽！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.38,0:10:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格拉迪亞是部優秀的機器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.68,0:10:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她只會混亂一刹那
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.75,0:10:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽住，趁那機會突破保護罩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.99,0:10:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米奇少爺！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.69,0:10:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停止，別過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.36,0:10:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.70,0:10:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.13,0:10:57.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他要運用最候僅餘的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.53,0:10:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成全他吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.03,0:11:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米奇！不行！停止！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.40,0:11:05.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉，能夠認識你，我很幸運
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.31,0:11:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對不會忘記你…！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.38,0:11:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絲莉亞拜託你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.42,0:11:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見，莉莉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.39,0:11:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米奇！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.81,0:12:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.45,0:12:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脫身了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.53,0:12:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.66,0:12:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米奇他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.13,0:12:38.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽了？米奇發生甚麽事！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.27,0:12:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在沒空問那種事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.77,0:12:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又開始聚合了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.47,0:12:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絲莉亞！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.94,0:12:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米奇！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.61,0:12:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米奇少爺！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.85,0:12:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！米奇！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.36,0:13:07.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉！米奇發生甚麽事！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.60,0:13:11.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才…米奇運用最候僅餘的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.10,0:13:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫我們…打開保護罩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.87,0:13:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎會的…！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.81,0:13:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我入去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.11,0:13:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉！等等！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.94,0:13:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我令米奇…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.11,0:13:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絲莉亞，你要消滅格拉迪亞吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.79,0:13:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無錯！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.47,0:13:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布烈絲…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.58,0:13:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是甚麽回事！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.15,0:14:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變成這樣子，他已經不想再活吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.72,0:14:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布烈絲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.62,0:14:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停手，求求你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.22,0:14:10.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的對手是亞人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.36,0:14:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.93,0:14:15.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你堅強了呢，莉莉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.23,0:14:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.70,0:14:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.45,0:14:34.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.22,0:14:37.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在…在這里，身體浮起来啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.45,0:14:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「超電導空間」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.82,0:14:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這里沒有重力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.83,0:14:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格拉迪亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.77,0:14:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絲莉亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.97,0:14:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的誕生是錯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.57,0:15:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是爸爸的錯誤啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.65,0:15:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.92,0:15:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是甚麽！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.83,0:15:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,費挪現象！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.46,0:15:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,費挪現象為何好像生物一樣！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.27,0:15:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若給它們碰到…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.94,0:15:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝甲服會馬上失常起来！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.14,0:15:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過来！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.98,0:15:40.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行！無效！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.58,0:15:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麽，沒法子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.62,0:15:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想做甚麽？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.69,0:15:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.86,0:15:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搜索這座塔內未截斷的能源喉管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.60,0:15:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知…知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.47,0:16:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我絕對不想這樣做…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.48,0:16:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布烈絲！很危險的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.94,0:16:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.54,0:16:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了，只有這里未截斷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.77,0:16:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上轉駁去你那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.58,0:16:44.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快…快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.58,0:16:50.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.59,0:16:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絲莉亞，莲娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.16,0:16:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.73,0:17:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.03,0:17:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布烈絲！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.13,0:17:06.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.80,0:17:42.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真嘔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.37,0:17:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒法子，你總是幹些危險的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.27,0:17:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無錯，竟然主動跟亞人粘在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.91,0:17:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真羅唆，剛才逼不得已吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.65,0:17:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絲莉亞呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.96,0:18:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格拉迪亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.89,0:18:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格拉迪亞！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.20,0:18:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的誕生是錯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.40,0:18:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說過吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.10,0:18:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奪去我爸爸生命的也是你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.41,0:18:21.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的外形為何會跟你相似的呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.14,0:18:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘管我是Antiseed時…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.45,0:18:28.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾給埋在你的腦內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.92,0:18:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也只是為了模仿你的腦機能吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.35,0:18:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我並非你女兒，亦非你的複製人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.09,0:18:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對，但你誕自我的身體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.29,0:18:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以，我要消滅你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.73,0:18:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本毋須維持這種外形
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.40,0:18:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家亦一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.17,0:18:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說甚麽！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.31,0:18:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亦毋須留在這種地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.34,0:18:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不會離開這里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.54,0:18:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會在這里永遠停止活動！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.42,0:19:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絲莉亞！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.69,0:19:14.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停止！說回人類的語言！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.66,0:19:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絲莉亞，你要消滅我嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.33,0:19:20.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米奇…！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.17,0:19:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也在她體內啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.54,0:19:26.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有亞人都有聯繫，是一個個體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.88,0:19:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米奇…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.92,0:19:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞人誕自絲莉亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.39,0:19:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以，亞人跟人類也有聯繫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.29,0:19:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變成跟我一樣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.22,0:19:45.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時，你便不用再痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.56,0:19:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.83,0:19:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚麽不是？莉莉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.70,0:19:50.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在說話的根本不是米奇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.03,0:19:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為米奇絕對無理由會那樣說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.04,0:19:56.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是格拉迪亞說的，絲莉亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.07,0:20:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好…！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.71,0:20:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做甚麽！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.11,0:20:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去，絲莉亞會有危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.92,0:20:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這隻怪物！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.73,0:20:21.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絲莉亞！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.07,0:20:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…米奇…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.54,0:20:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絲莉亞，振作！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.98,0:20:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚…甚麽事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.65,0:20:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道發生甚麽事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.93,0:20:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟發生甚麽事！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.47,0:21:06.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,積蒙塔…逐漸變成格拉迪亞！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.48,0:21:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可留在這里！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.11,0:21:15.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,積蒙塔…變成格拉迪亞！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.62,0:23:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不道德的女神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.26,0:23:59.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,張開巨大的黑色翅膀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.19,0:24:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備孕育新世代的生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.43,0:24:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被遺棄的舊生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.57,0:24:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能拼命掙扎嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.74,0:24:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格拉迪亞飛上宇宙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.41,0:24:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能有點魯莽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:13.31,0:24:14.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我們只好跟着去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:15.54,0:24:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回，吹波糖危機


